	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I got an old gameboy that i am applying some mods to.<br />I also have a broken Ds (screen cracked off) whichs battery i want to implant into my DMG.<br />I am not very familiar with how accumulators work, <br />So my question is if it is possible to add a DS accumulator to an<br /> old DMG gameboy and if yes, how it is done?<br />As far as i know there is some safety board which shold be in every accu to prevent overcharge.<br />Is there anything that has to be applied to the gameboy to be able to let it get powered from a ds li-ion accu and charge it at the same time?<br />Thanks in advance.

		

		</td>
